=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你係度開po唔會比人bam, 相反同樣既文章係果邊就bam撚左，明個分別未？ 都唔講大家係用戶體驗上既分別了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56950394c2ca3d685f72cc904c12a5aba629dbe1","tid":16654,"uid":38,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T16:54:40.000Z","msg":"請多咗人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"978d2965b39f4e34890ec8fe9487d446fbdf1a7f","tid":16654,"uid":33073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T16:57:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>請多咗人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無用架啦，高登已經成為歷史，係上一代既產物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40f75d9ae5f550fe317dc73bb2f5a8bb5d942ac7","tid":16654,"uid":17831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T16:59:06.000Z","msg":"諗住返去睇，load 幾秒入到去，再load 幾秒入到吹水區，然後就出error page<br />\n<br />\n點解我以前忍受到。。。。"},{"pid":"71c1789ede3cd0ab4948c054526f1236d1c74c13","tid":16654,"uid":41382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T17:00:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>請多咗人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你肯比返HKG PLUS 級別既iOS apps 來先啦，而家上都上唔撚到啊屌你"},